# PASSWORLD 🔐

PASSWORLD is a web-based, hacking-style password analyzer tool built with Python Flask.  
It analyzes password strength, breach status, cracking time, and entropy in real time — with a live animated Matrix-style background!

## ✨ Features
- Password Strength Evaluation (Weak / Moderate / Strong)
- Password Breach Check (using HaveIBeenPwned API)
- Crack Time Estimation
- Entropy Calculation
- Live Hacking-Style Background Animation

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Python 3
- Flask
- HTML5 / CSS3
- JavaScript (Canvas Animation)

## 🚀 How to Run Locally
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/PASSWORLD.git
cd PASSWORLD
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py